caption: The image is an Instagram post that features a colorful illustration of various fruits and vegetables, including apples, oranges, and pineapples. The post is captioned with a message about food waste, stating that when we throw out food, we not only waste a meal but also the water and energy that went into producing it. The post concludes with a call to action to visit the website reallygreatsite.com.
original_title: Blue Yellow Pink Organic Illustrative Climate Impact Square Food Waste Instagram Post
tags: impact of food waste on climate
texts: we don't just waste a meal.
We waste all the water and energy that went into producing it.
